{"_id":"y6dK4qajdKJI7tu8","name":"Cheat Sheet: Fortune","permission":{"default":0,"TnWyDcFgUQWxXpUx":3},"folder":"","sort":300001,"flags":{},"content":"<h1>Spend Fortune to:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a d20 on a result of &laquo; 1 &raquo; (Fortune spent before the roll)</li>\n<li>Perform an additional Standard Action</li>\n<li>Restore one Stress (Vigor or Resolve) to full</li>\n<li>Ignore all instances of a single Harm type until the end of the current Scene</li>\n<li>Influence the Story</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Regain Fortune from (max 5):</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Start of session (3 or 2) or an hour of play (1-3)</li>\n<li>Good roleplaying (1)</li>\n<li>Voluntary Failure (1 Doom Point + 1&nbsp;Fortune Point)</li>\n<li>Creating a Complication with a Trait&nbsp;of the character (1) &nbsp;</li>\n</ul>"}
{"_id":"y6dK4qajdKJI7tu8","name":"Cheat Sheet: Fortune","permission":{"default":0,"TnWyDcFgUQWxXpUx":3},"folder":"","sort":300001,"flags":{},"content":"<h1>Spend Fortune to:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a d20 on a result of &laquo; 1 &raquo; (Fortune spent before the roll)</li>\n<li>Perform an additional Standard Action</li>\n<li>Restore one Stress (Vigor or Resolve) to full</li>\n<li>Ignore all instances of a single Harm type until the end of the current Scene</li>\n<li>Influence the Story</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Regain Fortune from (max 5):</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Start of session (3 or 2) or an hour of play (1-3)</li>\n<li>Good roleplaying (1)</li>\n<li>Voluntary Failure (1 Doom Point + 1&nbsp;Fortune Point)</li>\n<li>Creating a Complication with a Trait&nbsp;of the character (1) &nbsp;</li>\n</ul>"}
{"_id":"Uyjl6lKuTW3mtSY3","name":"Condition: Poisoned","permission":{"default":0,"TnWyDcFgUQWxXpUx":3},"folder":"","sort":600001,"flags":{},"content":"<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; box-sizing: content-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">While each poison has a specific effect, the general effect is to grant the character the Staggered condition.</p>"}
